'''Mauritania''' ke naga lefasaneng la [[Afrika]]. ''Mauritania'' e leboabodikela la [[Afrika]], e wela seleteng sa [[Afrika Bodikela]].

''Mauritania'' e agišane le : 
* [[Senegal]] (borwabodikela),
* [[Mali]] (bohlabela le borwabohlabela),
* [[Algeria]] (leboabohlabela),
* [[Western Sahara]] (leboabodikela), bogolo bja naga e le [[Morocco]].

